LANG_CHINESE        "审判"

REFERENCE           LIGHTNING_STRIKE
LANG_ENGLISH        "Electric Judgement: "
LANG_CHINESE        "审判"

REFERENCE           FORCE_LIGHTNINGSTRIKE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Electric Judgement\nDuration: Instant\nArea Of Effect: Entire Environment\nEffect: Electric Judgment is a Force technique used by the Jedi to spray yellow electric bolts of variable intensity from the hands and fingers.\n\n"
LANG_CHINESE        "原力审判\n持续时间：即时\n效果范围：整个环境\n效果：是绝地使用的一种力量技能，从手和手指上喷射不同强度的黄色闪电。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_LIGHTNING_STRIKE_LVL1_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 1 - Jedi fires a burst of lightning able to travel a significant distance, causing very little damage."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 1 - 绝地发射一道闪电，能够传播很长的距离，造成很小的伤害。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_LIGHTNING_STRIKE_LVL2_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 2 - Jedi fires a burst of lightning able to travel a significant distance, causing minor damage and requires less concentration."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 2 - 绝地发射一道闪电，能够传播很长的距离，造成轻微的伤害，并需要较少的注意力。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_LIGHTNING_STRIKE_LVL3_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 3 - Jedi fires a burst of lightning able to travel a significant distance, causing moderate damage and requiring much less concentration."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 3 - 绝地武士发射一道闪电，能够传播很长的距离，造成中等程度的伤害，并需要更少的注意力。"

REFERENCE	    FEAR
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Fear:"
LANG_CHINESE        "恐惧"

REFERENCE	    FEAR2
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Fear"
LANG_CHINESE        "恐惧"

REFERENCE	    INGAME_FEAR2
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Fear"
LANG_CHINESE        "恐惧"

REFERENCE           FORCE_FEAR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Fear\nDuration: Indefinite\nArea Of Effect: Living persons only\nEffect: Jedi infects the victim's mind with the Dark Side of the Force, causing them to lash out in fear against allies and enemies alike.\n\n"
LANG_CHINESE        "原力恐惧\n持续时间：无限\n效果范围：仅限活人\n效果：绝地用原力的黑暗面感染受害者的心灵，使他们在恐惧中猛烈抨击盟友和敌人。\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_FEAR_LVL1_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 1 - Victim permanently lashes out against allies and enemies alike. Common enemies have a 50% chance to be affected, while Force Sensitives are almost impossible to affect."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 1 - 受害者永远猛烈攻击盟友和敌人。普通敌人有50%的几率受到影响，而原力敏感者几乎不可能受到影响。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_FEAR_LVL2_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 2 - Victim permanently lashes out against allies and enemies alike. Common enemies will be affected, while most force sensitives have a 5% chance of being affected. More powerful Jedi and Sith have a 1% chance of being affected."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 2 - 受害者永远猛烈攻击盟友和敌人。普通敌人会受到影响，而大多数对原力敏感者有5%的几率受到影响。更强大的绝地和西斯有1%的几率受到影响。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_FEAR_LVL3_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 3 - Victim permanently lashes out against allies and enemies alike. Common enemies will be affected, while most force sensitives have a 50% chance of being affected. More powerful Jedi and Sith have a 2% chance of being affected."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 3 - 受害者永远猛烈攻击盟友和敌人。普通敌人会受到影响，而大多数对原力敏感者有50%的几率受到影响。更强大的绝地和西斯有2%的几率受到影响。"

REFERENCE	    DEADLYSIGHT
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Deadly Sight:"
LANG_CHINESE        "凝视"

REFERENCE	    DEADLYSIGHT2
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Deadly Sight"
LANG_CHINESE        "凝视"

REFERENCE	    FORCE_DEADLYSIGHT_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Force Deadly Sight\nDuration: Instant\nArea of Effect: Near Jedi\nEffect: Force Deadly Sight is a power of the dark side of the Force, focusing the user's hatred into deadly energy.\n\n"
LANG_CHINESE        "原力凝视\n持续时间：即时\n效果范围：绝地周围\n效果：是原力黑暗面的力量，将使用者的仇恨集中到致命的能量中。\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_DEADLYSIGHT_LVL1_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 1 - By channeling this ability, a Force-user harnessed fury and hatred and then projected them through an intense glare onto the victim.The Deadly Sight will blister the skin and vaporize extremities."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 1 - 通过引导这种能力，原力使用者利用愤怒和仇恨，然后通过强烈的眩光将其投射到受害者身上。致命的凝视会使皮肤起泡并蒸发四肢。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_DEADLYSIGHT_LVL2_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 2 - By channeling this ability, a Force-user harnessed fury and hatred and then projected them through an intense glare onto the victim.The Deadly Sight will blister the skin and vaporize extremities."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 2 - 通过引导这种能力，原力使用者利用愤怒和仇恨，然后通过强烈的眩光将其投射到受害者身上。致命的凝视会使皮肤起泡并蒸发四肢。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_DEADLYSIGHT_LVL3_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 3 - By channeling this ability, a Force-user harnessed fury and hatred and then projected them through an intense glare onto the victim.The Deadly Sight will blister the skin and vaporize extremities."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 3 - 通过引导这种能力，原力使用者利用愤怒和仇恨，然后通过强烈的眩光将其投射到受害者身上。致命的凝视会使皮肤起泡并蒸发四肢。"

REFERENCE           BLAST
LANG_ENGLISH        "Blast: "
LANG_CHINESE        "爆炸"

REFERENCE           BLAST2
LANG_ENGLISH        "Blast"
LANG_CHINESE        "爆炸"

REFERENCE           FORCE_BLAST_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Force Blast\nDuration: Instant\nArea Of Effect: Entire Environment\nEffect: Jedi unleashes a concentrated telekinetic burst against their enemies, causing damage.\n\n"
LANG_CHINESE        "原力爆炸\n持续时间：即时\n效果范围：整个环境\n效果：绝地对敌人发动集中的远程能量爆发，并造成伤害。\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_BLAST_LVL1_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 1 - Jedi detonates a concentrated burst of force energy, causing little damage."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 1 - 绝地引爆集中爆发的原力能量，造成的伤害很小。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_BLAST_LVL2_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 2 - Jedi detonates a concentrated burst of force energy, causing minor damage."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 2 - 绝地武士引爆集中爆发的力量能量，造成轻微伤害。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_BLAST_LVL3_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 3 - Jedi detonates a concentrated burst of force energy, causing moderate damage."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 3 - 绝地武士引爆集中爆发的力量能量，造成中等伤害。"

REFERENCE	    INSANITY
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Insanity:"
LANG_CHINESE        "失常"

REFERENCE	    INSANITY2
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Insanity"
LANG_CHINESE        "失常"

REFERENCE	    FORCE_INSANITY_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Force Insanity\nDuration: Variable\nArea of Effect: Living persons only\nEffect: Allows Jedi to wrack mind of an enemy\n\n"
LANG_CHINESE        "原力失常\n持续时间：变量\n效果范围：仅限活人\n效果：能让绝地武士扰乱敌人的思想。\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_INSANITY_LVL1_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 1 - Jedi wracks the mind of a single enemy for 5 seconds."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 1 - 绝地武士在5秒内摧毁一个敌人的思想。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_INSANITY_LVL2_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 2 - Jedi wracks the mind of a single enemy for 10 seconds."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 2 - 绝地武士在10秒内摧毁一个敌人的思想。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_INSANITY_LVL3_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 3 - Jedi wracks the mind of a single enemy for 15 seconds. The enemy then dies."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 3 - 绝地武士在15秒内摧毁一个敌人的思想，然后敌人就死了。"

REFERENCE	    BLINDING
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Blinding:"
LANG_CHINESE        "致盲"

REFERENCE	    BLINDING2
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Blinding"
LANG_CHINESE        "致盲"

REFERENCE	    FORCE_BLINDING_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Force Blinding\nDuration: Variable\nArea of Effect: Living persons only\nEffect: Force blinding was a telekinetic light side Force power. Upon use of this technique, a blinding flash of energy emanated from a user's hand, manifesting as a flash of light that overloaded a target's vision, causing temporary blindness.\n\n"
LANG_CHINESE        "原力致盲\n持续时间：变量\n效果范围：仅限活人\n效果：是一种远程能量轻侧原力力量。使用这项技术后，使用者的手会发出一道耀眼的闪光，表现为一道闪光，使目标的视力过载，导致暂时失明。\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_BLINDING_LVL1_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 1 - A powerful tool of the light side, a Jedi could obfuscate an opponent's sight, making it difficult for the adversary to spot and attack the Jedi or anyone else."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 1 - 一个光明面的强大力量，绝地可以用来模糊对手的视线，使对手很难发现并攻击绝地武士或其他任何人。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_BLINDING_LVL2_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 2 - A powerful tool of the light side, a Jedi could obfuscate an opponent's sight, making it difficult for the adversary to spot and attack the Jedi or anyone else."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 2 - 一个光明面的强大力量，绝地可以用来模糊对手的视线，使对手很难发现并攻击绝地武士或其他任何人。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_BLINDING_LVL3_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 3 - A powerful tool of the light side, a Jedi could obfuscate an opponent's sight, making it difficult for the adversary to spot and attack the Jedi or anyone else."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 3 - 一个光明面的强大力量，绝地可以用来模糊对手的视线，使对手很难发现并攻击绝地武士或其他任何人。"

REFERENCE	    PROJECTION
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Projection:"
LANG_CHINESE        "投影"

REFERENCE	    PROJECTION2
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Projection"
LANG_CHINESE        "投影"

REFERENCE	    FORCE_PROJECTION_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH	    "Force Projection\nDuration: Variable\nArea of Effect: Jedi only\nEffect: Force projection, also known as Similfuturus, was a Fallanassi Force technique recorded in the sacred Jedi texts and utilized by Jedi Master Luke Skywalker during the Battle of Crait.\n\n"
LANG_CHINESE        "原力投影\n持续时间：变量\n效果范围：仅限绝地\n效果：也被称为Similfuturus，是一种法拉纳西力量技能，记录在神圣的绝地书籍中，绝地大师卢克 天行者在克雷特战役中使用。\n\n"

REFERENCE           FORCE_PROJECTION_LVL1_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 1 - The technique allows a Jedi to create an illusory doppelganger of themselves that could be transmitted through the Force across vast distances."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 1 - 这项技术可以让绝地创造出一个虚幻的替身，可以通过原力传播到固定的距离。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_PROJECTION_LVL2_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 2 - The technique allows a Jedi to create an illusory doppelganger of themselves that could be transmitted through the Force across vast distances."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 2 - 这项技术可以让绝地创造出一个虚幻的替身，可以通过原力传播到固定的距离。"

REFERENCE           FORCE_PROJECTION_LVL3_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rank 3 - The technique allows a Jedi to create an illusory doppelganger of themselves that could be transmitted through the Force across vast distances."
LANG_CHINESE        "等级 3 - 这项技术可以让绝地创造出一个虚幻的替身，可以通过原力传播到固定的距离。"

